headline: Hershey Stock: Is HSY Underperforming the Consumer Staples Sector?
summary: Hershey has underperformed the Consumer Staples sector over the past year, and analysts are cautious about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Shelf-Stable Food Q2 Earnings: Hershey (NYSE:HSY) is the Best in the Biz
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q2, starting with Hershey (NYSE:HSY).
